Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.21,0:00:02.65,中文,,0,0,0,,吸血鬼日记 前情提要\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Previously on "The Vampire Diaries"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.65,0:00:04.05,中文,,0,0,0,,达蒙死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Damon's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.05,0:00:06.54,中文,,0,0,0,,我要你让我忘记我曾经爱上过他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I want you to compel me to forget that I ever loved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.54,0:00:09.12,中文,,0,0,0,,-达蒙 萨尔瓦多是谁  -他是个恶魔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Who is Damon Salvatore? - He was a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.12,0:00:11.82,中文,,0,0,0,,-我们到底在哪儿 -1994年\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Where the hell are we? - 1994.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.82,0:00:13.05,中文,,0,0,0,,我们永远也出不去了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We're never getting out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.05,0:00:14.56,中文,,0,0,0,,有别人在这儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}There's someone else here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.56,0:00:15.79,中文,,0,0,0,,如果要回家 我们要用魔法古物\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}To get home, we'll harness the power
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.79,0:00:17.76,中文,,0,0,0,,控制好日蚀的能量\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}of the eclipse using a mystical relic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.76,0:00:19.08,中文,,0,0,0,,这叫做运星\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's called an ascendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.08,0:00:21.56,中文,,0,0,0,,-你又在做那件事 -什么事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- You're doing that thing again. - What thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.56,0:00:22.82,中文,,0,0,0,,像个贱人一样的那个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, the thing where you're a bitch
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.82,0:00:24.73,中文,,0,0,0,,因为你喜欢某个人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}because you like somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.73,0:00:26.00,中文,,0,0,0,,这是我的女朋友艾薇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That's my girlfriend Ivy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:28.31,中文,,0,0,0,,有人昨天晚上当着我的面杀了她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Somebody killed her last night right in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.86,0:00:30.17,中文,,0,0,0,,艾薇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ivy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:31.69,中文,,0,0,0,,你的朋友恩佐强迫我喝了他的血\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Your friend Enzo made me drink his blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.70,0:00:34.36,中文,,0,0,0,,现在我只觉得非常渴\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and now I'm just so thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:39.07,中文,,0,0,0,,吸血鬼杀了我妻子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Vampires murdered my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.07,0:00:42.32,中文,,0,0,0,,我要找到他 以及他所有的吸血鬼同伴\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I gonna get him to name all his vampire buddies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.10,0:01:02.84,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你好 - 嗨 我是特里普 库克\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Hello? - Hi. Tripp Cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.84,0:01:04.44,中文,,0,0,0,,只是想谢谢你把吸血鬼恩佐交给我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Just wanted to thank you for turning over
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.69,0:01:07.81,中文,,0,0,0,,他非常有用\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}that vampire Enzo to me. He's been very helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.27,0:01:10.81,中文,,0,0,0,,恩佐么 我以为 嗯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Enzo? I thought, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.81,0:01:12.56,中文,,0,0,0,,我以为你会杀了他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I thought you were supposed to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.57,0:01:17.38,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 我会的 在我知道他做过的所有事之后\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, I will eventually once I know everything he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.38,0:01:21.45,中文,,0,0,0,,-所以他告诉你什么了 -听起来好像神秘瀑布镇的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- So what has he told you? - Sounds like the vampire problem
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.46,0:01:24.59,中文,,0,0,0,,吸血鬼问题没有我想的那么严重\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}in Mystic Falls isn't as bad as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.59,0:01:27.29,中文,,0,0,0,,我是说 如果他知道一些名字 他会说出来的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I mean, if he had any names, he'd have given them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.29,0:01:28.46,中文,,0,0,0,,天知道我为了让他说话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Lord knows I've done plenty of things
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.46,0:01:29.71,中文,,0,0,0,,做了多少事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to get him to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.10,0:01:32.53,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 听起来不错\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, that's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.53,0:01:34.23,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 萨凡纳的事只是个意外\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah. Seems like it's moved on to Savannah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.23,0:01:35.80,中文,,0,0,0,,我已经把我的一些人派到下面去了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I've sent some of my guys down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.80,0:01:38.24,中文,,0,0,0,,他们会检查它 看看他们发现了什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}They're gonna check it out, see what they find.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:40.17,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢 嗯 谢谢你的提醒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Thanks for the, uh, heads-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.17,0:01:42.44,中文,,0,0,0,,创始人家族本来就是团结一心的 是吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Founding families got to stick together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.44,0:01:43.60,中文,,0,0,0,,必须的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.38,0:01:54.11,中文,,0,0,0,,艾薇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ivy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.26,0:01:59.59,中文,,0,0,0,,你是在装修吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You redecorated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.90,0:02:12.42,中文,,0,0,0,,我大约应该告诉你 我杀了你的老板迪恩\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I should probably tell you I killed your boss Dean.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.42,0:02:14.71,中文,,0,0,0,,他在林子里埋我的时候我醒来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I woke up when he was burying me in the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.72,0:02:19.91,中文,,0,0,0,,我喝干了他的血 但还是不够\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I drank every drop of his blood, but it wasn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:21.51,中文,,0,0,0,,是的 我知道那感觉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah. I know the feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.51,0:02:24.55,中文,,0,0,0,,-那你为什么不帮我 -我正在试着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Then why weren't you helping me? - I'm trying to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:27.12,中文,,0,0,0,,就给我两袋血和上了关于日光的一课\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Two blood bags and a lesson on sunlight?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.12,0:02:29.09,中文,,0,0,0,,哇 非常感谢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Wow! Thanks a million.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.09,0:02:30.66,中文,,0,0,0,,听着 我得把你带出萨凡纳\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Listen. I have to get you out of Savannah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.66,0:02:33.06,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 因为你我死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hey. I am dead because of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.06,0:02:35.31,中文,,0,0,0,,因为你没有告诉我你是什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}because you lied to me about who you were,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:37.11,中文,,0,0,0,,因为你的朋友恩佐把我转变成了什么东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}because your friend Enzo turned me into something
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:39.23,中文,,0,0,0,,就像吸血鬼猎人巴菲里面的角色\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}straight out of "Buffy the vampire slayer."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.23,0:02:40.93,中文,,0,0,0,,艾薇 淡定 当你变成吸血鬼之后\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ivy, calm down. When you're a vampire,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:42.40,中文,,0,0,0,,你的情绪会被放大\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}your emotions are heightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.41,0:02:43.95,中文,,0,0,0,,原来你也知道 看看我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You think?! Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:45.44,中文,,0,0,0,,我曾经是个有头有脸的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I used to be a decent person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.44,0:02:48.29,中文,,0,0,0,,我的成绩很好 回家过圣诞节\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I got good grades, I when home for Christmas,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:49.98,中文,,0,0,0,,我有个很棒的工艺品店\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I had a fricking etsy store!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.98,0:02:52.51,中文,,0,0,0,,-艾薇 拜托 -然后我现在成了杀人凶手\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Ivy, please. - And now I am a killer,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.51,0:02:56.18,中文,,0,0,0,,我要做的就是杀人 杀更多的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and all I am gonna do is kill more and more,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:02:59.30,中文,,0,0,0,,这都是你的错\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and it's all your fault.
