Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:23.20,中文,,0,0,0,,-斯特凡 你怎么 -我需要你帮我个忙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Stefan? Where have you... - I need a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.04,0:03:27.75,中文,,0,0,0,,你在做什么 这个箱子又是怎么回事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What are you doing, and what is with this trunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.75,0:03:28.70,中文,,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.82,0:03:32.06,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 天哪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:34.02,中文,,0,0,0,,我在哪儿 你做了什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Where I am I? What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:37.46,中文,,0,0,0,,-艾薇 这是怎么回事 -嗯 恩佐转化了他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Ivy? How did this happen? - Uh, Enzo turned her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.47,0:03:40.75,中文,,0,0,0,,然后斯特凡扭断了我的脖子 我醒过来就在箱子里了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Then Stefan broke my neck, and I woke up in a trunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.76,0:03:43.16,中文,,0,0,0,,对 所以我需要你忙个小忙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Right. So I need a little bit of help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:45.55,中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:47.20,中文,,0,0,0,,不 不 不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No. No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:48.63,中文,,0,0,0,,只是看着她一小会儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Just watch her for a little while
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.63,0:03:50.30,中文,,0,0,0,,我要去找卢克帮她做一个日光戒指\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}while I get Luke to make her a daylight ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.30,0:03:53.57,中文,,0,0,0,,给她看看绳子 教她控制自己 拜托了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Show her the ropes, teach her some control, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.57,0:03:55.01,中文,,0,0,0,,不 不 这个烂摊子和我没关系\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No, no. This is not my mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.01,0:03:56.27,中文,,0,0,0,,这是你的烂摊子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This is your mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.28,0:03:57.38,中文,,0,0,0,,如果你不来找我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}A mess that wouldn't have happened
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:58.58,中文,,0,0,0,,它根本不会发生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}if you had just left me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:03:59.81,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 我能听见你们说话 你们知道吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Uh, I can hear you, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.81,0:04:03.15,中文,,0,0,0,,我能听见很多东西 非常清晰的那种\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I can hear everything, like, perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:05.72,中文,,0,0,0,,需要我提醒你这附近\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Do I need to remind you that there is a vampire hunter
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:07.08,中文,,0,0,0,,有吸血鬼猎人吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}lurking around?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.09,0:04:09.39,中文,,0,0,0,,他不在这儿 他在萨凡纳 这就是为什么我们不在那里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He's not here. He's in Savannah, which is why we're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:10.86,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道最悲剧的是什么吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You know the real tragedy in all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.86,0:04:12.72,中文,,0,0,0,,我看到 他只是没那么喜欢你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I read "He's just not that into you," And...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.72,0:04:14.03,中文,,0,0,0,,闭嘴\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.03,0:04:16.06,中文,,0,0,0,,听着 特里普库克不知怎么的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Look. Tripp Cook has somehow decided
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:20.04,中文,,0,0,0,,变成了西边沿海地区自封的吸血鬼猎人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to become the eastern seaboard's self-proclaimed vampire hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:23.13,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我们不能控制好自己 我们都有危险\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}None of us are safe if we can't control ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.14,0:04:25.63,中文,,0,0,0,,如果有人能教会她 那就是你了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}If anybody can teach her, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:27.17,中文,,0,0,0,,是么 嗯 你不用恭维我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah? Well, you don't have to flatter me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:28.54,中文,,0,0,0,,因为我已经知道了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}because I already know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.54,0:04:30.51,中文,,0,0,0,,好吗 只要几个小时\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}All right? So just a couple of hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.51,0:04:34.95,中文,,0,0,0,,然后你就再也不用看到我了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and then you'll never have to deal with me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.95,0:04:39.15,中文,,0,0,0,,你以为这就是我想要的么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Is that what you think I want?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.15,0:04:40.72,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道 你来说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I don't know. You tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.29,0:04:46.95,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.43,0:04:59.07,中文,,0,0,0,,我们什么时候吃东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}When do we eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.01,0:05:03.37,中文,,0,0,0,,返校活动\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}"Homecoming."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:06.05,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 举手表决\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}All right. By a show of hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.05,0:05:08.61,中文,,0,0,0,,谁知道今晚返校活动的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}who knows the supernatural origin
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:12.48,中文,,0,0,0,,超自然起源\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}of tonight's homecoming party?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:15.59,中文,,0,0,0,,一个南北战争时期的战士 内森 惠特莫尔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}A civil war soldier Nathan Whitmore
