Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.32,0:05:53.79,中文,,0,0,0,,但是故事还在继续\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But the legend goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:57.72,中文,,0,0,0,,那位惠特莫尔女士每年这天的晚上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That lady Whitmore is out on this night
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:06:02.60,中文,,0,0,0,,都会穿着有她爱人血的白衣服\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}every year dressed in white, covered in her lover's blood,
