Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:06:59.76,中文,,0,0,0,,我正准备接受这个建议\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and I intend on taking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.76,0:07:01.12,中文,,0,0,0,,今晚派对上我能看到你么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Am I gonna see you at the party tonight?
