Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.17,0:07:14.94,中文,,0,0,0,,我呆在家就很舒服\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I am perfectly content staying at home,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:16.57,中文,,0,0,0,,让我的头发长出来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}letting my hair grow out.
