Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:31.78,中文,,0,0,0,,这些年你第一次有好心情\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You're in a good mood for the first time this decade.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.78,0:08:33.85,中文,,0,0,0,,因为我今晚要和我的女孩约会\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Because I have a hot date with my girl tonight.
