Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:18.22,中文,,0,0,0,,尽管他这几个月一直无视我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}who didn't ignore me for months
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:21.26,中文,,0,0,0,,然后一有事需要帮忙就利用我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and then use me when they need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.26,0:10:24.46,中文,,0,0,0,,哇 终于知道了为什么斯特凡要带我来这\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Whoa. Just realized why Stefan brought me here
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:26.16,中文,,0,0,0,,跟你学学怎么自我控制了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to learn control.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:27.90,中文,,0,0,0,,对自己好点吧 解开束缚吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Do yourself a favor. Unwind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:31.40,中文,,0,0,0,,承认你对他有感觉不就行了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Just admit you have a thing for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:33.04,中文,,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.74,0:10:35.20,中文,,0,0,0,,我看到了你过来吃晚饭那晚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I saw the way you looked at him
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:36.54,中文,,0,0,0,,你看他的眼神\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}that night you came over for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.54,0:10:38.81,中文,,0,0,0,,你还为他切东西吃\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You practically cut his food for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.81,0:10:41.54,中文,,0,0,0,,你不懂 我们之间的关系\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh! You know, my relationship with Stefan
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:44.65,中文,,0,0,0,,真的是太 复杂了 好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}is strictly... Complicated, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.65,0:10:45.65,中文,,0,0,0,,你不是应该在练习熟悉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Aren't you supposed to be practicing
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:47.85,中文,,0,0,0,,成为吸血鬼还是什么的吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}your vamping or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.85,0:10:50.55,中文,,0,0,0,,练好了 看到了吗 我很好啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Done. See? I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.55,0:10:51.79,中文,,0,0,0,,你已经把你的号码存在了我的手机里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You already put your number into my phone
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:54.05,中文,,0,0,0,,让我有突发状况就联系你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}as my emergency vampire contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.06,0:10:55.49,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道我一晒到阳光就会灼痛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I know I burn in the sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.49,0:10:57.76,中文,,0,0,0,,我们可以迫使别人 把他们抓来 吸完血 抹除记忆就了事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}we covered compulsion and snatch, eat, erase.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:10:59.59,中文,,0,0,0,,天快黑了 快走吧 去参加派对\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Look. It's getting dark. Let's go party.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:02.96,中文,,0,0,0,,你可以顺便教我怎么吸血又不会致死\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You can teach me how to eat someone without killing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.96,0:11:05.12,中文,,0,0,0,,斯特凡就要到了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Stefan will be here very soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.12,0:11:08.40,中文,,0,0,0,,到时候在他的陪同下你想干什么都可以\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and then you can do whatever you want with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:09.94,中文,,0,0,0,,那我们至少可以下下棋\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Can we at least play a board game
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:12.38,中文,,0,0,0,,或者做些和吸血鬼没关系的事吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}or do something non-vampire related.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:13.64,中文,,0,0,0,,终于出了一个好主意\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Finally a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.64,0:11:15.38,中文,,0,0,0,,你想玩什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What kind of game do you want to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.38,0:11:17.46,中文,,0,0,0,,我也不知道 拼字\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I don't know. Scrabble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.47,0:11:19.05,中文,,0,0,0,,我有锦标赛型 经典型\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I have tournament, classic,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.05,0:11:20.71,中文,,0,0,0,,还有旅游适配型\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and travel-sized.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.77,0:11:48.27,中文,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:56.78,中文,,0,0,0,,拉芙林医生怎么也在这\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What's Dr. Laughlin doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.78,0:11:58.81,中文,,0,0,0,,看起来好火辣\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Looking hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:12:01.13,中文,,0,0,0,,我还以为她会永远穿着那件白大褂呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I thought the lab coat was permanently attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:02.76,中文,,0,0,0,,是我邀请她来的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I invited her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:04.42,中文,,0,0,0,,想为她牵线搭桥\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's kind of a setup,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.42,0:12:07.47,中文,,0,0,0,,只是他们双方都不知道而已\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}only neither party knows about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:09.97,中文,,0,0,0,,走吧 去展现你的迷人风采\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Come on, time to get your Kansas on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz358.9\move(580,242,553,420,24,1025)} {\fn微软雅黑\fs60\b1\c&HA6A8AA&}{\move(120,160,93,160)}玉米地迷宫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:24.04,中文,,0,0,0,,斯特凡 我已经给你发了三条短信\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Stefan, hey. This is the third message
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.04,0:12:26.64,中文,,0,0,0,,通知你你的小蛇精病吸血鬼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}alerting you that your psychotic little she-vamp
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:28.28,中文,,0,0,0,,已经去嗨皮了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}has gone AWOL,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.28,0:12:30.38,中文,,0,0,0,,还有你得知道 外面已经天黑了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and if you hadn't noticed, it's dark outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:34.04,中文,,0,0,0,,所以今晚如果有女生死了的话 所有帐都要算在你头上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}so every dead sorority girl tonight is officially on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:52.50,中文,,0,0,0,,在另辟蹊径吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Grading on the curve, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:54.31,中文,,0,0,0,,喝酒根本没什么用\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You know, this barely makes a dent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.70,0:12:57.44,中文,,0,0,0,,不过也值得一试\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Can't fault me for trying, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:58.69,中文,,0,0,0,,想要来一点吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.69,0:13:02.91,中文,,0,0,0,,不了 我只是过来跟卢克拿一个这个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No. I just came here to get one of these from Luke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.91,0:13:04.81,中文,,0,0,0,,我来猜一猜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Let me guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.81,0:13:09.82,中文,,0,0,0,,你是在想 达蒙死了 这都是我的错\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You played the "Damon is dead, and it's all your fault" Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:11.53,中文,,0,0,0,,你想干嘛 斯特凡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What do you want, Stefan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.54,0:13:15.04,中文,,0,0,0,,恩佐和卡罗琳找到我后 他转化了一个吸血鬼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Enzo turned a vampire when he and Caroline found me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.04,0:13:17.46,中文,,0,0,0,,你是说你那个萨凡纳的女朋友\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You mean your girlfriend from Savannah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:21.53,中文,,0,0,0,,那个你骗我 让我以为她是个巫师\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The one you falsely led me to believe
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:25.17,中文,,0,0,0,,可以帮达蒙和邦妮复活的女生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}was a witch who knew how to help Damon and Bonnie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.17,0:13:27.07,中文,,0,0,0,,她叫艾薇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Her name's Ivy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:31.27,中文,,0,0,0,,我希望你能帮我催眠她去理解掌握好这一切\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I was hoping you can compel her to get a handle on things,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.27,0:13:34.68,中文,,0,0,0,,还有让她离开我 去过她的新生活\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}get somewhere far away from me, live a good life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:36.58,中文,,0,0,0,,你是在叫我帮你和她分手吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Are you asking me to help you with a breakup?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:38.58,中文,,0,0,0,,我只是希望你能给她一个全新的生活\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm just asking you to give her a fresh start.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:41.98,中文,,0,0,0,,是给你一个全新的生活吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You mean give you a fresh start.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.99,0:13:44.29,中文,,0,0,0,,对不起 斯特凡 没有你想的那么简单\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Sorry, Stefan. It's not that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.29,0:13:45.59,中文,,0,0,0,,你催眠埃琳娜忘记达蒙的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, it was when you compelled Elena
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:46.92,中文,,0,0,0,,也不是很难啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to forget about Damon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:49.82,中文,,0,0,0,,是你先忘了他的 兄弟\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Well, you forgot about him first, pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.83,0:13:51.16,中文,,0,0,0,,他是我哥\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He was my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.16,0:13:54.49,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 他也是我最好的朋友\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah, and he was my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:56.43,中文,,0,0,0,,在我催眠你变回我之前认识的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Why don't you get out of my face
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.43,0:13:58.13,中文,,0,0,0,,斯特凡之前\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}before I compel you to be the guy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:13:59.91,中文,,0,0,0,,我劝你赶紧走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I used to know instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.99,0:14:22.48,中文,,0,0,0,,你吓到我了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.48,0:14:25.66,中文,,0,0,0,,真的吗 哪有那么可怕\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Really? That wasn't scary,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.66,0:14:27.28,中文,,0,0,0,,不过这个就可怕了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:28.73,中文,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.67,0:14:38.95,中文,,0,0,0,,好了 我抓了一个人 吸了血\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}There. I snatched, I ate,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:41.29,中文,,0,0,0,,现在抹除记忆就行了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}now erase.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:42.96,中文,,0,0,0,,什么抹除记忆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Erase what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.05,0:14:45.45,中文,,0,0,0,,你到底在对我做了什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What the hell are you doing to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.45,0:14:49.05,中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得我可能做错了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I-I don't think I did it right,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:51.65,中文,,0,0,0,,而且我也还没喝饱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and I'm still hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:53.93,中文,,0,0,0,,老天 我一定会杀了你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, my God. I am totally gonna kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.93,0:14:57.79,中文,,0,0,0,,你快跑 跑 我说真的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You should go, run. Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:04.48,中文,,0,0,0,,我逊毙了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I suck at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:08.84,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 你知道很有可能这个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hey! You know there's a very probable chance
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:10.53,中文,,0,0,0,,坟墓是你挖给自己的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}you're digging your own grave
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:13.31,中文,,0,0,0,,算了不说了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and not bothered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:19.15,中文,,0,0,0,,哈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.51,0:15:23.12,中文,,0,0,0,,看来我回来的正是时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Looks like I got back just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:29.12,中文,,0,0,0,,垃圾摇滚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Zima, grunge,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:32.43,中文,,0,0,0,,流行的亚历克斯新秀卡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}every Alex Rodriguez rookie card in demand,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:34.29,中文,,0,0,0,,还有一个传呼机 你开什么玩笑\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and a pager. Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.30,0:15:37.20,中文,,0,0,0,,号码555你好凯伊 我怎么舍得丢下这些好东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}555-Hiya-Kai. No way I'm giving those digits up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:38.87,中文,,0,0,0,,这些就是你去拿的重要东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}These were the important supplies you had to get?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:40.43,中文,,0,0,0,,未来听起来很好玩 好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Look. The future sound great, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.44,0:15:42.31,中文,,0,0,0,,我对互联网也超级期待\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm superexcited about the Internet,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.31,0:15:45.23,中文,,0,0,0,,但是我大部分时间都是在1994年\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but 1994 has been my home for most of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:47.01,中文,,0,0,0,,所以带这些以解思乡之情\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'd hate to get homesick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:50.04,中文,,0,0,0,,-所以我们现在下去吧 -不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- So let's get down there. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:55.52,中文,,0,0,0,,在你告诉我咒语之前我们哪也不去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We are not going anywhere until you show me the spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:57.20,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:05.39,中文,,0,0,0,,我们真的是哪也不去吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Are we literally not going anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.39,0:16:07.49,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 你不想告诉我咒语\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Fine. You don't want to show me the spell,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:09.03,中文,,0,0,0,,那你就自己来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}then you can do it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:11.13,中文,,0,0,0,,想要我的魔力\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You want my magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:14.40,中文,,0,0,0,,你就拿走吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.40,0:16:16.97,中文,,0,0,0,,哇哦 她真的努力在装成很勇敢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Heh. Uh-oh. She's being brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:18.44,中文,,0,0,0,,我是认真的 凯伊 你最大的隐患不就是这个吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm serious, Kai. This was your big threat,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:19.71,中文,,0,0,0,,不是吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.71,0:16:21.31,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我不念咒语 我们出不去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}If I don't do the spell and let us out of here,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.31,0:16:22.88,中文,,0,0,0,,你就会拿走我的魔力自己施展\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}you'll just take my magic, leave me for dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:26.48,中文,,0,0,0,,不管我死活 现在就动手吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and do the spell yourself. So go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.48,0:16:28.94,中文,,0,0,0,,全都拿走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Take all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:32.42,中文,,0,0,0,,我真拿了你可别介意\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Don't mind if I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:35.39,中文,,0,0,0,,邦妮\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Bonnie?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:37.32,中文,,0,0,0,,没事的 我不会死的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's ok. He won't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:39.41,中文,,0,0,0,,在我看来可不像是这样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Doesn't look like that from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:40.49,中文,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ohh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:41.89,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 邦妮\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hey, Bonnie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:43.33,中文,,0,0,0,,哇 你这家伙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Whoa, hey, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:44.66,中文,,0,0,0,,住手\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.07,0:16:57.88,中文,,0,0,0,,他根本不知道咒语\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He doesn't know the spell,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:17:02.18,中文,,0,0,0,,意味着 我们用不着他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}which means we don't need him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.19,0:17:03.43,中文,,0,0,0,,[咒语]\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Motus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:07.27,中文,,0,0,0,,不要 不要\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.27,0:17:08.73,中文,,0,0,0,,邦妮\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Bonnie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.29,0:17:15.13,中文,,0,0,0,,做得好 邦妮\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Great work, Bonnie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:21.13,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 我认出来了这个稻草人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh! I think I recognize this scarecrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.13,0:17:24.30,中文,,0,0,0,,每个稻草人你都是这么说的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You've said that about every scarecrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:28.67,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 看来我们真的是迷路了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ok. Well, then we are officially lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.68,0:17:30.98,中文,,0,0,0,,事实上 左转两次再右转三次就能出去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Actually, it's 2 lefts and 3 rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:32.31,中文,,0,0,0,,进来之前\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I pulled up a satellite image
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.31,0:17:34.01,中文,,0,0,0,,我截图了一个卫星图像\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}of this maze before I came.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.01,0:17:36.25,中文,,0,0,0,,哇 你是热衷于竞赛的类型 我懂了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh. Competitive type. Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.25,0:17:38.93,中文,,0,0,0,,问题是 我是不是你喜欢的类型\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Question is, am I your type?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.02,0:17:42.05,中文,,0,0,0,,说真的 真不是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Honestly, no,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.06,0:17:45.36,中文,,0,0,0,,但是人是会变的 是不是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but people can change, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.36,0:17:46.89,中文,,0,0,0,,哇哦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:48.14,中文,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:49.73,中文,,0,0,0,,你还是对你的前男友念念不忘\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You're still hung up on your ex.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.73,0:17:51.63,中文,,0,0,0,,野心勃勃的医科生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Overly ambitious premed student,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:53.87,中文,,0,0,0,,急于成为医生好证明给前男友看\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}desperate to become a doctor so she can prove
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.87,0:17:56.97,中文,,0,0,0,,甩了她是犯了多大的错误\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to the guy who dumped her that he messed up big time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:17:59.84,中文,,0,0,0,,事实上 他死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Actually, he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.84,0:18:01.84,中文,,0,0,0,,或者差不多那样子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Or that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.84,0:18:05.04,中文,,0,0,0,,-对不起 我还以为斯特凡是 -他不是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Sorry. I thought Stefan was... - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.04,0:18:08.08,中文,,0,0,0,,-好吧 -嗯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Nice. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.08,0:18:10.32,中文,,0,0,0,,没事 没事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's ok, it's ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.32,0:18:15.29,中文,,0,0,0,,他叫达蒙 但是今晚不属于他的事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}His name was Damon, but tonight isn't about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.29,0:18:17.25,中文,,0,0,0,,今晚属于你和我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's about you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.06,0:18:25.03,中文,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.03,0:18:28.81,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 一点都不好笑\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ohh! Not cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.27,0:18:31.27,中文,,0,0,0,,哈哈哈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Heh heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:34.84,中文,,0,0,0,,波旁酒教授 来得真是时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, Professor Bourbon. Perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:36.88,中文,,0,0,0,,我还以为你早就在急救室见惯了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Imagine you see a lot worse in E.R.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:38.31,中文,,0,0,0,,我在那看到的都是自然存在的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Everything I see there is natural,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.31,0:18:39.48,中文,,0,0,0,,虽然恶心 但是不是人为化妆的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}gross but natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.48,0:18:42.74,中文,,0,0,0,,僵尸 鬼魂 不死人 这些一点都不酷\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Zombies, ghosts, the undead not cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.74,0:18:44.38,中文,,0,0,0,,是这样子啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Good to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.38,0:18:46.65,中文,,0,0,0,,你有没有在这见到过埃琳娜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You haven't seen Elena around here, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.65,0:18:49.62,中文,,0,0,0,,今晚可以说是她恐吓我来的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She basically blackmailed me into coming tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.62,0:18:51.96,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 我来猜猜 她叫你走出教室\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh. Let me guess. She told you to get out of the classroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.96,0:18:52.96,中文,,0,0,0,,享受一下生活\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}live a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.46,0:18:54.46,中文,,0,0,0,,哇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Aw.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.46,0:18:56.59,中文,,0,0,0,,她想撮合我们 好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We're being set up. Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:18:59.23,中文,,0,0,0,,现在你就有点绅士风度 帮我离开这里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Now why don't you be a gentleman and get me the hell out of here
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.23,0:19:00.63,中文,,0,0,0,,因为我们实在是太老了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}because we are way too old for this party,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:03.34,中文,,0,0,0,,而且我想去喝一杯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and I need a drink stat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:10.14,中文,,0,0,0,,-我还以为你是个洁癖鬼 -这次就破一下例\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- I thought you were a germaphobe. - I'll make an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs40\\frz331.3\pos(808,338)}这派对好烂\N给你5分钟过来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.08,0:19:31.26,中文,,0,0,0,,我告诉你会很好玩的 是不是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}See? I told you it would be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.54,0:20:03.00,中文,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.22,0:20:20.25,中文,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:29.30,中文,,0,0,0,,救命啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.30,0:20:35.00,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 嘿 嘿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hey, hey, hey. Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.35,0:20:46.88,中文,,0,0,0,,埃琳娜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Elena!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.88,0:20:51.65,中文,,0,0,0,,埃琳娜 过来这边\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Elena, get over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.65,0:20:53.74,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 天哪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, God. Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.75,0:20:55.62,中文,,0,0,0,,情况多严重\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}H-how bad is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.59,0:21:01.16,中文,,0,0,0,,好的 我来吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ok. I got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.16,0:21:03.30,中文,,0,0,0,,你也做不了什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm not sure there's anything you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.30,0:21:04.83,中文,,0,0,0,,我会尽我所能的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'll do everything that I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.83,0:21:07.09,中文,,0,0,0,,去看看别人需不需要帮忙 好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Just go see if you can help someone else, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.23,0:21:12.31,中文,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Come on. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.71,0:21:33.24,中文,,0,0,0,,听我说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.25,0:21:35.43,中文,,0,0,0,,你躲得很是时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You dove out of the way just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.43,0:21:37.10,中文,,0,0,0,,你真是命硬 现在赶紧走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You were very lucky. Now get out of here
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.10,0:21:39.30,中文,,0,0,0,,能带走多少人带走多少\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and take as many people as you can, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.30,0:21:40.58,中文,,0,0,0,,走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.34,0:21:46.63,中文,,0,0,0,,泰勒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Tyler?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.64,0:21:49.14,中文,,0,0,0,,-我刚才开着车 埃琳娜 -什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- I was driving the truck, Elena. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.14,0:21:50.68,中文,,0,0,0,,这个家伙迎面向我冲过来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This guy ran right in front of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.68,0:21:52.78,中文,,0,0,0,,现在他受伤很严重\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and he's hurt bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.78,0:21:54.91,中文,,0,0,0,,如果他死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}If he dies,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.92,0:21:56.28,中文,,0,0,0,,我又会变成狼人了 知道吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm a werewolf all over again, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.28,0:21:57.68,中文,,0,0,0,,我需要你过来帮我 我们在一条沟里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I need you to get here. We're in a ditch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.68,0:21:59.49,中文,,0,0,0,,我也不知道这是哪里 但是你得过来帮我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I don't know where, but I need you here now,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.49,0:22:00.72,中文,,0,0,0,,求你了 快过来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}so please hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.72,0:22:01.89,中文,,0,0,0,,泰勒 你不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Tyler, you don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.89,0:22:03.73,中文,,0,0,0,,你的车冲过了迷宫\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You drove right through the maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.74,0:22:06.59,中文,,0,0,0,,现在这里到处都是受伤的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}There are injured people everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.59,0:22:09.13,中文,,0,0,0,,那我应该怎么做\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What the hell am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.13,0:22:12.30,中文,,0,0,0,,听着 别挂\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Just... listen. Just hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.30,0:22:14.78,中文,,0,0,0,,你得让他醒着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Um, make sure that you keep him awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.79,0:22:17.87,中文,,0,0,0,,看看他伤得多重 我去找乔和阿拉里克\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Assess his injuries while I go find Jo and Alaric.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.18,0:22:24.51,中文,,0,0,0,,你在流血\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You're bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.51,0:22:25.71,中文,,0,0,0,,我没事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.71,0:22:28.68,中文,,0,0,0,,你有事 我看看\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No, you're not. Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.68,0:22:31.18,中文,,0,0,0,,等等 怎么回事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Wait. What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.18,0:22:32.89,中文,,0,0,0,,那应该不是我的血\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I don't think it's my blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.89,0:22:35.52,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 干起活来又得多费些手脚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh. Ok. That's gonna make things more difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.52,0:22:37.39,中文,,0,0,0,,我得带你出去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I really think I should get you out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.40,0:22:39.82,中文,,0,0,0,,不 我不能走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No. That's not an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.61,0:22:44.03,中文,,0,0,0,,你脸色怎么这么苍白 你晕血吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You look pale. Does blood make you squeamish?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.03,0:22:45.36,中文,,0,0,0,,是 有一点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah. Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.37,0:22:47.15,中文,,0,0,0,,不用担心 你会习惯的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Don't worry. You'll get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.16,0:22:50.61,中文,,0,0,0,,-报警 跟紧我 -好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Call 911, follow me. - Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.22,0:23:08.30,中文,,0,0,0,,谢天谢地\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Thank God!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.30,0:23:09.52,中文,,0,0,0,,你把她弄丢了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You lost her?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.52,0:23:10.76,中文,,0,0,0,,所以你是几百万小时过后\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, so you decide to listen to your messages
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.76,0:23:12.42,中文,,0,0,0,,才看短信的吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}a million hours later?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.43,0:23:14.73,中文,,0,0,0,,不 我没有弄丢她 是她扭了我的脖子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No. I didn't lose her. She snapped my neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.73,0:23:17.06,中文,,0,0,0,,-你怎么这么久 -我有事做\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- What the hell took you so long? - I got caught up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.06,0:23:18.60,中文,,0,0,0,,你有什么事做\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You got caught up, doing what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.60,0:23:22.34,中文,,0,0,0,,-当时我已经开车走了 -你要走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Driving halfway out of town. - You were leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.57,0:23:25.60,中文,,0,0,0,,我把日光戒指放在了你的门前\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I slid Ivy's daylight ring under your front door.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.61,0:23:29.07,中文,,0,0,0,,我不在乎什么狗屁戒指 斯特凡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No! I don't care about some stupid ring, Stefan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.08,0:23:31.28,中文,,0,0,0,,你真的想把你的吸血鬼前女友\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Were you seriously about to dump
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.28,0:23:33.21,中文,,0,0,0,,丢在我这\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}your vampire ex-girlfriend onto my lap
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.70,0:23:35.36,中文,,0,0,0,,然后你就脱身离开\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and then just skip town?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.08,0:23:40.72,中文,,0,0,0,,天哪 你现在到底变成了什么人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}God, who are you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.72,0:23:42.35,中文,,0,0,0,,我变成了努力想过新生活的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm someone who's trying to start over,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.35,0:23:45.00,中文,,0,0,0,,但是你和恩佐突然出现\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and then suddenly, you and Enzo show up,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.00,0:23:46.69,中文,,0,0,0,,害到我现在被人追着跑\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and now I have hunters on my trail
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.69,0:23:48.33,中文,,0,0,0,,还有个新生吸血鬼想要杀了我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and a brand-new vampire who wants to kill me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.33,0:23:50.21,中文,,0,0,0,,还有她沿途遇到的所有人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and everyone else in her path,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.22,0:23:52.76,中文,,0,0,0,,这还让我怎么重新开始 卡罗琳\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and that's not how someone starts over, Caroline.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.57,0:23:58.39,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道最糟糕的事情是什么吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You know what the worst part about all of this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.39,0:24:01.07,中文,,0,0,0,,一个月以前 我希望达蒙能够回来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Is about a month ago, I wished that Damon would come back
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.07,0:24:03.73,中文,,0,0,0,,因为我知道这样的话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}because I knew if that happened
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.73,0:24:07.08,中文,,0,0,0,,你也会回来的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}that I'd get you back, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.08,0:24:08.95,中文,,0,0,0,,但是现在 我唯一希望的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but right now, all I want is for you
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.95,0:24:12.23,中文,,0,0,0,,就是你赶紧回到车上然后滚蛋\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to just get back in your car and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.11,0:24:34.24,中文,,0,0,0,,你在哪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.24,0:24:35.67,中文,,0,0,0,,我做了一件坏事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I did a really bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.67,0:24:38.22,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 你是指折断我的脖子吗 这我已经知道了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, you mean, break my neck? Yeah. I noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.22,0:24:42.10,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 那就是两件 听着 我很抱歉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ok. Two bad things. Look. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.10,0:24:44.28,中文,,0,0,0,,告诉我你的确切位置然后在原地等我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Tell me exactly where you are and stay put,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.28,0:24:46.31,中文,,0,0,0,,我这就来找你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and I'll come get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.65,0:24:49.19,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 嗯 嗯 嗯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Mmm. Mmm, mmm, mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.65,0:24:52.42,中文,,0,0,0,,你能不能消停一会儿让我好好集中注意力\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Can you stop and let me concentrate?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.91,0:24:55.36,中文,,0,0,0,,往好处想 这表示这东西不赖\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}On the bright side, this stuff's not so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.37,0:24:57.73,中文,,0,0,0,,还是水果味儿汽水\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's fruity and fizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.73,0:24:59.33,中文,,0,0,0,,达蒙 我还有事要忙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Damon, I'm working on something.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.33,0:25:01.60,中文,,0,0,0,,往坏处想 这表示你智商堪忧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}On the not so bright side is your intelligence
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.60,0:25:03.27,中文,,0,0,0,,因为你毁了我们唯一能够离开这的机会\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}because you took the only chance
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.27,0:25:04.47,中文,,0,0,0,,还把他变成了一个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}of us getting out of here and turned him
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.47,0:25:06.97,中文,,0,0,0,,巨大的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}into a giant...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.97,0:25:08.21,中文,,0,0,0,,尸串\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Douchekabob.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.21,0:25:09.63,中文,,0,0,0,,你想一下 达蒙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Think about it, Damon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.63,0:25:11.58,中文,,0,0,0,,什么样的监狱会给囚犯钥匙呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What prison gives an inmate a key?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.58,0:25:13.08,中文,,0,0,0,,这是个脑筋急转弯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Is that a trick question,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.08,0:25:15.11,中文,,0,0,0,,还是这东西真的开始奏效了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}or is this stuff actually starting to kick in?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.11,0:25:16.32,中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得双子座女巫聚会\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I think the Gemini coven
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.32,0:25:18.43,中文,,0,0,0,,用贝内特的咒语创造了这个地方\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}used a Bennett spell to create this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.43,0:25:20.28,中文,,0,0,0,,万一这就是为什么外婆把我送到这来的原因呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What if that's why my grams sent me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.29,0:25:24.39,中文,,0,0,0,,一般我听不懂你在说什么的时候我都会摆出这副表情\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This is the face I make when I don't understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.14,0:25:31.64,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 我外婆对我说过的最后一句话就是要保持强大\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You know, the last thing my grams said to me was to stay strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.10,0:25:35.00,中文,,0,0,0,,她会不会就是在告诉我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What if that was her way of telling me
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.00,0:25:36.53,中文,,0,0,0,,我有能力出去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I have the power to get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.53,0:25:37.87,中文,,0,0,0,,我有运星\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I have the ascendant,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.87,0:25:40.24,中文,,0,0,0,,可以看到许多天文现象\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}a massive celestial event to draw from,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.25,0:25:43.03,中文,,0,0,0,,再加上想早日摆脱掉你的欲望\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}plus a burning desire to get away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.66,0:26:02.76,中文,,0,0,0,,怪不得凯不会杀掉我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That's why Kai wouldn't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.56,0:26:06.36,中文,,0,0,0,,他需要贝内特女巫\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He needed a Bennett.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.36,0:26:09.02,中文,,0,0,0,,只有我才能让他离开这里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I was his only way out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.48,0:26:14.00,中文,,0,0,0,,喂 你要去哪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Whoa. Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.00,0:26:16.17,中文,,0,0,0,,回家\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Home.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.17,0:26:17.57,中文,,0,0,0,,来吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.92,0:26:45.26,中文,,0,0,0,,-怎么了 -我把这孩子给撞了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- What happened? - I hit this kid in the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.59,0:26:50.35,中文,,0,0,0,,不是我的错 只是一场意外\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It wasn't my fault. It was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.36,0:26:53.27,中文,,0,0,0,,恩 不过也是件好事 对吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah, but that's a good thing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.28,0:26:58.03,中文,,0,0,0,,-你知道我什么意思 -无所谓了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- You know what I mean. - It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.04,0:26:59.57,中文,,0,0,0,,如果他死掉的话 我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}If he dies, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.51,0:27:04.24,中文,,0,0,0,,打给埃琳娜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Call Elena.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.40,0:27:07.00,中文,,0,0,0,,救护车已经在路上了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ambulances are on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.00,0:27:09.83,中文,,0,0,0,,好的 过来 我需要你帮助\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Good. Get over here. I need your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.23,0:27:11.04,中文,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.13,0:27:14.94,中文,,0,0,0,,把手放在这 这样能止住血\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Put your fingers right here. That should stop the bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.94,0:27:17.31,中文,,0,0,0,,这样我好检查他其它部位\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}While I can look at the rest of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.57,0:27:21.76,中文,,0,0,0,,-你还好吧 -恩 我很好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Are you doing ok? - Yeah, I'm fine. Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.76,0:27:23.95,中文,,0,0,0,,用手压住股动脉就行了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Just keep your finger on that femoral artery.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.95,0:27:24.95,中文,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.02,0:27:28.35,中文,,0,0,0,,他的脉冲正在下降\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}His pulse is still dropping.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.35,0:27:29.72,中文,,0,0,0,,你不是第一次遇到这种情况吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This isn't your first rodeo?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.72,0:27:31.52,中文,,0,0,0,,听着 我上完医学院之后参加过军队\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Listen, I was in the army right out of med school.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.52,0:27:33.94,中文,,0,0,0,,家庭原因 那时只想着逃避\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Family stuff. Just had to get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.70,0:27:43.07,中文,,0,0,0,,拉芙琳医生 我的朋友泰勒 他遇到麻烦了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Dr. Laughlin, my friend Tyler, he's in trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.07,0:27:45.95,中文,,0,0,0,,听起来很糟糕 而且我不知道他在哪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and its sounds really bad, and I don't know where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.95,0:27:47.74,中文,,0,0,0,,叫我乔就行 把扬声器打开\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Call me Jo. Put him on speaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.75,0:27:48.92,中文,,0,0,0,,好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.92,0:27:51.84,中文,,0,0,0,,-泰勒 听得见吗 -我不知道该怎么做\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Tyler, can you hear me? - I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.84,0:27:53.04,中文,,0,0,0,,他应该是失去意识了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I think he's losing consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.04,0:27:55.34,中文,,0,0,0,,我要你准确地回答我的问题\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Need you to answer my questions as accurately as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.35,0:27:57.81,中文,,0,0,0,,-出血了吗 -很多\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Is there blood? - Tons.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.81,0:27:59.05,中文,,0,0,0,,现在还在流血吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Is it still flowing? Is he bleeding now?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.05,0:28:01.28,中文,,0,0,0,,不 看起来没有在流血了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No. I... it looks like it stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.28,0:28:03.12,中文,,0,0,0,,他的鼻子或嘴巴里有没有出血\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Is there any coming out of his nose or his mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.12,0:28:04.15,中文,,0,0,0,,有\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.15,0:28:06.32,中文,,0,0,0,,什么颜色 红的还是黑的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What color is it? Is it red, or is it black?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.32,0:28:08.80,中文,,0,0,0,,黑色的 黑的很吓人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's black. It's really freaking black.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.81,0:28:12.43,中文,,0,0,0,,-我们要怎么做 -握着他的手\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- What do we do? - Take his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.50,0:28:18.00,中文,,0,0,0,,然后呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.00,0:28:20.34,中文,,0,0,0,,试着让他感觉好点就行\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Just try and keep him comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.34,0:28:21.87,中文,,0,0,0,,撑不了多久了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Won't be long now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.18,0:29:07.02,中文,,0,0,0,,是时候了 达蒙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's time, Damon.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.02,0:29:11.35,中文,,0,0,0,,很好 又要尴尬了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}All right. Let's get awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.33,0:29:16.52,中文,,0,0,0,,这样吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.53,0:29:18.03,中文,,0,0,0,,恩\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.33,0:29:22.56,中文,,0,0,0,,我敢肯定要是有的选 你选择任何人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm sure there are about a billion people
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.57,0:29:24.36,中文,,0,0,0,,也不会选我和你一起在这里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}you're rather be here with.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.50,0:29:29.81,中文,,0,0,0,,不一定\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.54,0:29:33.85,中文,,0,0,0,,走吧 啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Let's go... ohh!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.01,0:29:37.51,中文,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Unh!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.51,0:29:39.05,中文,,0,0,0,,你们是不是忘了谁\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Forgetting someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.74,0:29:49.11,中文,,0,0,0,,你们真的以为\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Did you really think I hadn't tried
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.11,0:29:50.48,中文,,0,0,0,,我以前没有试过自杀吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}to kill myself before?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.48,0:29:54.24,中文,,0,0,0,,我试过 很多次\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Because I had, lots of times,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.25,0:29:56.42,中文,,0,0,0,,各种方式\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}lots of ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.13,0:30:01.13,中文,,0,0,0,,你要是拿那个 下只箭就瞄准她的心脏了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Grab that, and the next arrow goes in her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.13,0:30:03.25,中文,,0,0,0,,选择吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.03,0:30:07.40,中文,,0,0,0,,我在这 没事了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.40,0:30:09.17,中文,,0,0,0,,不 噢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No! Ohh!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.18,0:30:11.30,中文,,0,0,0,,达蒙 不要\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Damon! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.22,0:30:23.86,中文,,0,0,0,,加油 老兄 求你了 一定要活下去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Come on, man. Please, you've got to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.32,0:30:26.53,中文,,0,0,0,,加油啊 兄弟\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Come on, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.53,0:30:30.66,中文,,0,0,0,,坚持住 你不能死\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Come on, man. You can't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.66,0:30:33.73,中文,,0,0,0,,够了 泰勒 停手\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Stop! Tyler, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.73,0:30:36.00,中文,,0,0,0,,停手吧 好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Just stop, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.00,0:30:37.91,中文,,0,0,0,,已经没有办法了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}There's nothing you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.27,0:30:43.90,中文,,0,0,0,,我杀了他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.91,0:30:45.29,中文,,0,0,0,,不 你没有\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No, you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.30,0:30:47.82,中文,,0,0,0,,是我杀了他 丽芙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yes, I did, Liv.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.88,0:30:51.61,中文,,0,0,0,,我们已经做了能做的一切\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Everything we've tried to do to keep me from this,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.61,0:30:55.89,中文,,0,0,0,,没想到这家伙突然会跑到路中间来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and all it took was one guy running out into the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.86,0:31:00.14,中文,,0,0,0,,你在做什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.15,0:31:02.81,中文,,0,0,0,,丽芙 不要 住手\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Liv, stop, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.82,0:31:04.86,中文,,0,0,0,,你这是在做什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.34,0:31:23.48,中文,,0,0,0,,你没有杀他 泰勒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You didn't kill him, Tyler.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.48,0:31:25.00,中文,,0,0,0,,是我杀的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.55,0:31:34.49,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 救护车来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hey. The ambulances have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.49,0:31:36.32,中文,,0,0,0,,乔说让医护人员把她抬走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Jo said to let the paramedics take it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.32,0:31:37.68,中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得她可能等不了了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I don't think she can wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.79,0:31:41.03,中文,,0,0,0,,她的气管已经\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Her windpipe, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.03,0:31:42.13,中文,,0,0,0,,学术上讲叫偏移\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Deviated is the medical term.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.13,0:31:43.80,中文,,0,0,0,,其实就是扭曲了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Screwed is more like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.80,0:31:45.80,中文,,0,0,0,,不管怎样 她现在很缺氧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Either way, she's not getting enough air.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.80,0:31:47.40,中文,,0,0,0,,利亚姆 我能帮忙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Liam, I can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.40,0:31:49.77,中文,,0,0,0,,很好 把她的头按住然后我来疏通她的气管\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Good. Stabilize her head while I trache her.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.21,0:31:53.95,中文,,0,0,0,,你之前做过吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Have you ever done this before?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.95,0:31:56.84,中文,,0,0,0,,用西柚实验过 不算成功\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Practiced on a grapefruit. Didn't end well.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.84,0:31:58.24,中文,,0,0,0,,不 利亚姆 我不是这个意思\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No, Liam. That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.25,0:31:59.74,中文,,0,0,0,,其实我可以\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I can actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.42,0:32:09.59,中文,,0,0,0,,成功了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.93,0:32:18.66,中文,,0,0,0,,-你真的做到了 -不用这么惊讶\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- You actually did it. - You don't sound so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.15,0:33:10.15,中文,,0,0,0,,邦妮 离开这儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Bonnie, get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.15,0:33:11.69,中文,,0,0,0,,我出不去了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm not gonna make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.70,0:33:13.11,中文,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Unh!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.62,0:33:17.32,中文,,0,0,0,,但你可以\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But you are. Motus.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.03,0:33:25.70,中文,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.67,0:33:30.08,中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.09,0:33:31.60,中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.91,0:33:37.41,中文,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.85,0:33:42.85,中文,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ohh.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.41,0:33:57.84,中文,,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}How you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.85,0:33:59.15,中文,,0,0,0,,你真的想知道吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You really want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.15,0:34:00.86,中文,,0,0,0,,我刚吃了几片止疼药\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Because I'm hopped up on pain meds
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.87,0:34:03.08,中文,,0,0,0,,想告诉你各种恶心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and just obnoxious enough to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.08,0:34:06.59,中文,,0,0,0,,我会慢慢听的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'll take my chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.59,0:34:09.02,中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得你很伟大\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I think you're great.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.02,0:34:11.79,中文,,0,0,0,,勇敢 幽默风趣\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You're brave, funny,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.79,0:34:14.19,中文,,0,0,0,,大概是我见过的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}not to mention maybe the most attractive man
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.19,0:34:16.70,中文,,0,0,0,,最有吸引力的男人了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I've ever seen,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.70,0:34:19.10,中文,,0,0,0,,我毫不避讳的告诉你这些\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and I feel completely comfortable telling you this
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.10,0:34:21.13,中文,,0,0,0,,因为我已经成熟并且知道自己想要什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}because I'm old enough to know what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.14,0:34:24.67,中文,,0,0,0,,你可能认为我疯了 不过我觉得我是注定了要认识你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And call me crazy, but I think I was meant to know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.41,0:34:30.69,中文,,0,0,0,,现在该你说点什么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This is the part where you say something
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.69,0:34:35.55,中文,,0,0,0,,或者亲一下 或转头就走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}or kiss me or run for the hills.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.55,0:34:37.73,中文,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.32,0:34:44.87,中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得你很聪明伶俐\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I think you're amazing, brilliant,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.58,0:34:48.83,中文,,0,0,0,,是我见过的最性感的女人之一\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and one of the sexiest women I have ever met,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.83,0:34:52.26,中文,,0,0,0,,并且我相信 你和我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and I would love to believe that you and I
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.27,0:34:53.79,中文,,0,0,0,,原本是天造地设的一对\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}were meant to be
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.80,0:34:55.70,中文,,0,0,0,,因为我知道除了我现在所过的生活之外\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}because I would love to believe there was a plan for me
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.70,0:34:58.76,中文,,0,0,0,,我还有一个别的计划\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}other than this life that I am living right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.68,0:35:06.05,中文,,0,0,0,,但是今晚很不愉快\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But tonight was a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.05,0:35:09.52,中文,,0,0,0,,你觉得我很无聊 还是个酗酒者\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You thought I was boring and a borderline alcoholic,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.52,0:35:13.35,中文,,0,0,0,,因为你还不了解我 还不了解真正的我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and because you don't know me, not the real me anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.35,0:35:15.22,中文,,0,0,0,,所以你不打算亲我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}you don't want to kiss me,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.22,0:35:18.48,中文,,0,0,0,,你非常希望我能够转头就走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and you absolutely want me to run for the hills.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.69,0:35:23.96,中文,,0,0,0,,你说的对\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.96,0:35:26.06,中文,,0,0,0,,今晚真的很不愉快\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Tonight was a literal disaster,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.07,0:35:28.62,中文,,0,0,0,,你完完全全就是个酗酒者\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and you're definitely an alcoholic...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.24,0:35:38.58,中文,,0,0,0,,但你一点也不无聊 里克\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But you're far from boring, Ric.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.49,0:35:51.19,中文,,0,0,0,,你在哪 我已经站在这好久了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Where are you? I have been standing here
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.19,0:35:52.92,中文,,0,0,0,,感觉像过了一个世纪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}for a hundred years.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.93,0:35:56.16,中文,,0,0,0,,别大惊小怪的 我快到了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Don't exaggerate. I'm almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.83,0:36:10.12,中文,,0,0,0,,要帮忙吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Need any help?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.31,0:36:17.96,中文,,0,0,0,,我听说学校里发生了一场不小的意外\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I heard about the, uh, big campus accident on my scanner.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.97,0:36:20.22,中文,,0,0,0,,有人受伤了还是怎么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I heard someone got hurt or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.22,0:36:21.67,中文,,0,0,0,,我很好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.68,0:36:23.05,中文,,0,0,0,,不会吧 你在流血呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Actually, you're bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.06,0:36:24.39,中文,,0,0,0,,不可能受到惊吓了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You might be in shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.39,0:36:25.86,中文,,0,0,0,,赶紧走吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Please just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.86,0:36:27.89,中文,,0,0,0,,我不能\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I don't think...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.77,0:36:32.40,中文,,0,0,0,,这样就行了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.82,0:36:36.80,中文,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.45,0:36:51.02,中文,,0,0,0,,那个穿得像惠特莫尔小姐的女的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So that girl dressed like lady Whitmore,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.02,0:36:53.02,中文,,0,0,0,,我都准备放弃她了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I was ready to give up on her,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.02,0:36:56.55,中文,,0,0,0,,但你能够救她 为什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and you were able to save her. How?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.56,0:36:58.82,中文,,0,0,0,,我也不知道 新手运气比较好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I don't know. Beginner's luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.82,0:37:01.13,中文,,0,0,0,,埃琳娜 她应该已经死了的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Elena, she should have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.13,0:37:03.83,中文,,0,0,0,,但她没死\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And she didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.83,0:37:08.43,中文,,0,0,0,,这个世界上有很多疯狂神秘的事情\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}There are crazy, mysterious things in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.43,0:37:10.84,中文,,0,0,0,,就连科学也无法解释\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I mean, some things science can't explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.84,0:37:12.87,中文,,0,0,0,,举个例子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Name one.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.87,0:37:15.41,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ok. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.41,0:37:17.34,中文,,0,0,0,,为什么婴儿要做第一次呼吸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Why does a baby take its first breath?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.34,0:37:20.21,中文,,0,0,0,,一种反应能力 一个新的肺里的液体\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}A reflex. The fluid in a newborn's lungs are...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.91,0:37:33.49,中文,,0,0,0,,我原本以为亲我比死亡更可怕\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I thought kissing me was a fate worse then death.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.49,0:37:37.16,中文,,0,0,0,,你之前问我喜欢什么样的类型\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You asked me what my type is.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.17,0:37:41.92,中文,,0,0,0,,今晚你就是个英雄 完全令人瞠目结舌\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You were a hero tonight, an absolutely jaw-dropping
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.92,0:37:46.27,中文,,0,0,0,,绝无仅有的英雄\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and out-of-this-world hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.27,0:37:47.59,中文,,0,0,0,,我就喜欢这样的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That's my type.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.25,0:37:58.27,中文,,0,0,0,,我们关门了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We're closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.27,0:37:59.75,中文,,0,0,0,,我和埃琳娜谈过\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I talked to Elena.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.75,0:38:01.85,中文,,0,0,0,,关门了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Still closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.85,0:38:04.32,中文,,0,0,0,,她说其他人都活了下来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}She said everyone else lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.72,0:38:07.29,中文,,0,0,0,,你不想和我谈谈都发生了什么吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You don't want to talk about what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.29,0:38:09.33,中文,,0,0,0,,没有什么好说的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I've got nothing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.80,0:38:14.49,中文,,0,0,0,,今晚你杀了人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You killed someone tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.33,0:38:18.40,中文,,0,0,0,,你不可能假装什么都没发生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You can't just pretend that didn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.77,0:38:26.71,中文,,0,0,0,,- 看看我 - 丽芙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Watch me. - Liv.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.26,0:38:30.34,中文,,0,0,0,,丽芙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Liv.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.18,0:38:36.69,中文,,0,0,0,,他死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.69,0:38:38.76,中文,,0,0,0,,你没有办法救活他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}There was nothing you could have done to save him,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.76,0:38:41.96,中文,,0,0,0,,所以你决定拯救我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}so you saved me instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.67,0:38:52.74,中文,,0,0,0,,是你救了我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.75,0:38:55.24,中文,,0,0,0,,无论我做什么也报答不了你这份情义\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I can never repay you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.24,0:39:00.88,中文,,0,0,0,,我所能做的就是答应你 决不浪费你的心意\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}All I can do is promise you that I won't waste it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.47,0:39:26.27,中文,,0,0,0,,哈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ahh.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.18,0:39:34.58,中文,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.41,0:39:38.49,中文,,0,0,0,,这都是真的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This is happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.50,0:39:41.78,中文,,0,0,0,,我要对着这个放着我家人尸体\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm gonna talk out loud to a...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.79,0:39:45.09,中文,,0,0,0,,的地窖自言自语了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}A crypt filled with my dead family.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.69,0:39:53.20,中文,,0,0,0,,除了你 达蒙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Everyone but you, Damon.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.20,0:39:56.83,中文,,0,0,0,,因为不管你在哪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Because wherever you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.83,0:39:58.43,中文,,0,0,0,,你都不会在这\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}it's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.01,0:40:05.71,中文,,0,0,0,,我必须得说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I got to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.48,0:40:11.58,中文,,0,0,0,,没有你我过得并不那么好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm not doing so great without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.18,0:40:16.92,中文,,0,0,0,,我一直试着重新开始\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I keep trying to start over,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.92,0:40:18.42,中文,,0,0,0,,但是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.79,0:40:21.56,中文,,0,0,0,,我无法做到\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I can't get anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.59,0:40:27.73,中文,,0,0,0,,因为我还是很茫然 哥哥\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Because I'm lost, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.94,0:40:34.77,中文,,0,0,0,,我很困惑\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.68,0:40:48.55,中文,,0,0,0,,那又怎样 离开了几个月而已\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So what? Gone a couple of months,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.55,0:40:49.89,中文,,0,0,0,,你就可以这样浪费\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}you think it's ok to waste a perfectly good
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.89,0:40:51.69,中文,,0,0,0,,这么上好的波旁威士忌吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}bottle of Bourbon?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.46,0:40:56.43,中文,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Ahh.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.43,0:40:59.93,中文,,0,0,0,,-达蒙 -是我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Damon? - Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.93,0:41:02.53,中文,,0,0,0,,活生生的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}In the flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.53,0:41:06.73,中文,,0,0,0,,-我现在怎么可能看到你 -因为我还没死 斯特凡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- How can I see you right now? - Because I'm not dead, Stefan.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.76,0:41:12.61,中文,,0,0,0,,我说 这酒是挺好 但比不上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I mean, this stuff's good, but it's not
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.61,0:41:14.14,中文,,0,0,0,,我看到了死人 那种感觉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}"I see dead people" Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.14,0:41:15.84,中文,,0,0,0,,哼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.31,0:41:20.88,中文,,0,0,0,,说来话长 弟弟\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's a hell of a long story, brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.88,0:41:24.22,中文,,0,0,0,,总而言之我回来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.16,0:41:29.66,中文,,0,0,0,,我回来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.16,0:41:37.57,中文,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.24,0:41:46.84,中文,,0,0,0,,我回来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm back.
